Hip Hop Pantsula's alleged wife Lerato Sengadi and his business partner Seabelo Modibe are at each other's throats over the Samas Lifetime Achievement Award Sengadi plans to receive on behalf of the late superstar. Sengadi announced that she would receive the gong on behalf of the fallen star at the Samas which will be held at Sun City on Saturday. TO READ MORE ON THIS STORY GET A COPY OF TODAY'S SUNDAY WORLD.